{"type": "article", "id": 24375, "title": "将硬币分类的存钱罐", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-24T07:00:21Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 97, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702142122MpGkwWVEhusj2NR4.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">存钱罐似乎很少使用，但放零碎硬币的盒子倒是很常见。泰国设计工作室 Studio Make Sense 发明了一个可以将硬币按大小分类的木盒子，投放硬币的孔后面是一个斜坡滑梯，按照银币的大小做了漏孔，对应了四个筒，这样不同的硬币就能集中掉进自己的筒里了。如果需要取出硬币，就把盒子打开。对于硬币种类更丰富的地方来说很实用。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142119NCbRue6IwBEpUSVF.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"1.25333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142120YeIy94Ssmchf0AF5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021421206FOMQrfDmJiIT1BN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.60555556\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142121Wej4tVrC8HD1yupb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68425926\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142121v1N4nXcsSDjMU6zF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.855\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}